♪ Zulu zambalu ♪

831
00:45:31,464 --> 00:45:33,003
♪ Zulu bashika ♪

832
00:45:33,027 --> 00:45:34,701
♪ Zum gali gali gali zum, gali gali zum ♪

833
00:45:34,738 --> 00:45:36,700
♪ Gali gali gali zum, gali gali zum ♪

834
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:46,972
Akela, you did well.

835
00:45:47,009 --> 00:45:48,067
You did well.

836
00:45:48,092 --> 00:45:49,347
You did well.

837
00:46:07,340 --> 00:46:08,340
Hey.

838
00:46:08,824 --> 00:46:10,820
You don't have to dress so neatly.

839
00:46:11,180 --> 00:46:12,340
No one's going to punish you.

840
00:46:12,670 --> 00:46:13,670
Come on.

841
00:46:14,360 --> 00:46:15,483
Since I'm wearing this,

842
00:46:15,501 --> 00:46:16,689
I have to wear it properly.

843
00:46:17,300 --> 00:46:18,947
I take fun seriously.

844
00:46:27,650 --> 00:46:29,156
I'm sorry about my friends.

845
00:46:29,869 --> 00:46:31,426
They didn't mean to look down on you.

846
00:46:31,990 --> 00:46:33,507
They just grew up differently.

847
00:46:40,680 --> 00:46:42,424
Are you embarrassed
that you brought me here?

848
00:46:42,449 --> 00:46:44,440
Embarrassed? No.

849
00:46:44,710 --> 00:46:47,926
I'd rate your creativity 100 out of 100.

850
00:46:51,430 --> 00:46:53,670
I really don't know what to talk about
with your friends.

851
00:46:54,280 --> 00:46:56,012
I tried to be funny to hide it,

852
00:46:56,800 --> 00:46:58,289
thinking it would win them over.

853
00:46:58,840 --> 00:47:01,273
Hey, you don't have to try anything.

854
00:47:01,316 --> 00:47:03,138
Just being yourself is enough.

855
00:47:03,390 --> 00:47:04,449
They'll get used to it.

856
00:47:13,013 --> 00:47:15,605
I'd rate your sexiness in this outfit
100 out of 100 too.

857
00:47:16,400 --> 00:47:19,993
I happen to be naturally sexy,

858
00:47:20,024 --> 00:47:21,452
so I don't need much dressing up.

859
00:47:27,260 --> 00:47:28,147
Come on.

860
00:47:28,172 --> 00:47:29,812
It's almost time to blow out the candles.

861
00:47:30,220 --> 00:47:31,169
I need to use the bathroom for a second.

862
00:47:31,193 --> 00:47:32,193
I need to poop.

863
00:47:32,620 --> 00:47:33,740
I'll catch up with you soon,

864
00:47:33,930 --> 00:47:34,930
Mr. Little Bunny.

865
00:47:43,230 --> 00:47:48,984
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

866
00:47:50,627 --> 00:47:51,627
Blow it out.

867
00:48:00,840 --> 00:48:02,430
Lion, what are you doing here?

868
00:48:04,430 --> 00:48:07,987
Well, I come here with you every year.

869
00:48:08,660 --> 00:48:10,966
I remember all your friends' birthdays.

870
00:48:11,021 --> 00:48:13,224
Look, I'm dressed right on theme.

871
00:48:13,255 --> 00:48:14,255
The letter B, right?

872
00:48:15,220 --> 00:48:16,246
British Royal.

873
00:48:16,700 --> 00:48:20,529
I've brought Pailin a birthday gift too.

874
00:48:20,560 --> 00:48:21,944
Open it.

875
00:48:22,410 --> 00:48:25,058
Oh! Lion!

876
00:48:25,370 --> 00:48:27,390
I've been looking for this bag for so long.

877
00:48:27,433 --> 00:48:28,960
How did you know?

878
00:48:29,230 --> 00:48:30,622
Kanit's friends are my friends too.

879
00:48:30,646 --> 00:48:31,796
I pay attention.

880
00:48:31,963 --> 00:48:32,996
Oh!

881
00:48:33,200 --> 00:48:35,372
Pailin, give it back to Lion.

882
00:48:35,710 --> 00:48:37,298
If you want it, I'll buy one for you.

883
00:48:39,020 --> 00:48:41,144
Lion, you should leave.

884
00:48:41,400 --> 00:48:42,800
My friends and I are partying here.

885
00:48:43,060 --> 00:48:44,455
Please don't ruin the mood.

886
00:48:45,680 --> 00:48:47,532
I want to talk to you again

887
00:48:49,200 --> 00:48:50,707
in front of all your friends.

888
00:48:50,744 --> 00:48:51,433
Everyone,

889
00:48:51,740 --> 00:48:52,996
please be my witness.

890
00:48:55,523 --> 00:49:00,934
I want you to know
I'm also hurting over what happened.

891
00:49:01,944 --> 00:49:03,940
I've reflected on myself

892
00:49:05,240 --> 00:49:06,440
and realized that, in the end,

893
00:49:07,940 --> 00:49:09,421
the one I want to be with

894
00:49:11,021 --> 00:49:13,020
and the one who can make me the happiest

895
00:49:14,500 --> 00:49:15,500
is you.

896
00:49:16,609 --> 00:49:18,689
There won't be a second
or a third person in my life.

897
00:49:20,250 --> 00:49:23,027
We'll travel the world together.

898
00:49:23,810 --> 00:49:26,369
I'm a captain. You're a flight attendant.

899
00:49:29,320 --> 00:49:32,787
No one suits me better than you.

900
00:49:35,910 --> 00:49:36,910
Kanit…

901
00:49:40,043 --> 00:49:41,043
Don't tell me…

902
00:49:41,320 --> 00:49:42,375
Don't tell me…

903
00:49:42,406 --> 00:49:42,843
Oh!

904
00:49:42,867 --> 00:49:43,867
Oh!

905
00:49:44,100 --> 00:49:45,100
Oh.

906
00:49:48,000 --> 00:49:49,000
Oh.

907
00:49:49,027 --> 00:49:50,027
He's proposing.

908
00:49:55,370 --> 00:49:56,553
Will you marry me?

909
00:49:59,180 --> 00:50:01,329
What's going on? Aww!

910
00:51:02,310 --> 00:51:03,310
What's up?

911
00:51:03,580 --> 00:51:05,987
(Where are you? I'm waiting
to have a drink with you.)

912
00:51:07,260 --> 00:51:08,260
I'm running an errand.

913
00:51:08,590 --> 00:51:11,510
(What errand? Just admit you're out
with your flight attendant boyfriend.)

914
00:51:11,640 --> 00:51:12,760
Like hell he's my boyfriend!

915
00:51:14,250 --> 00:51:16,141
I'm on my way. Bye.

916
00:51:29,260 --> 00:51:30,260
Hey.

917
00:51:31,180 --> 00:51:32,775
You left the party without telling me.

918
00:51:37,580 --> 00:51:38,580
What are you doing here?

919
00:51:42,200 --> 00:51:43,720
You looked so caught up in the moment.

920
00:51:44,030 --> 00:51:45,110
I didn't want to interrupt.

921
00:51:45,790 --> 00:51:49,169
Caught up? It was just a proposal.

922
00:51:55,650 --> 00:51:56,726
It's your dream, isn't it?

923
00:51:57,510 --> 00:51:59,870
For that captain to get down on one knee
and propose to you.

924
00:52:01,649 --> 00:52:03,640
That's right. That was my dream.

925
00:52:06,960 --> 00:52:09,446
But not anymore.

926
00:52:18,250 --> 00:52:19,250
I'm sorry,

927
00:52:21,790 --> 00:52:23,187
but I don't think I can marry you.

928
00:52:24,400 --> 00:52:25,400
Why not?

929
00:52:26,400 --> 00:52:27,809
I've completely given in to you.

930
00:52:28,960 --> 00:52:30,418
But I can't trust you anymore.

931
00:52:31,840 --> 00:52:33,840
I don't want a relationship
built on suspicion.

932
00:52:35,230 --> 00:52:36,313
Besides,

933
00:52:37,430 --> 00:52:39,033
I'm done choosing what looks right.

934
00:52:40,680 --> 00:52:42,455
I'm choosing peace of mind.

935
00:52:54,240 --> 00:52:56,818
Who'd want to marry
someone who makes you cry?

936
00:52:57,980 --> 00:53:01,169
I want to be with someone
who makes me laugh

937
00:53:01,193 --> 00:53:02,344
and makes me happy.

938
00:53:02,720 --> 00:53:05,156
That someone doesn't need to
take me to fancy restaurants.

939
00:53:06,560 --> 00:53:10,307
It's not easy for me to
find someone like you.

940
00:53:14,252 --> 00:53:15,532
What's with this big confession?

941
00:53:15,925 --> 00:53:16,940
Are you proposing to me?

942
00:53:17,180 --> 00:53:18,676
I'm just here to tell you that,

943
00:53:19,280 --> 00:53:22,929
don't be discouraged by
your circumstances just yet.

944
00:53:23,560 --> 00:53:24,830
You still have a chance.

945
00:53:25,490 --> 00:53:26,490
What chance?

946
00:53:27,292 --> 00:53:29,290
A chance to ask me out.

947
00:53:34,650 --> 00:53:35,810
Then what are we waiting for?

948
00:53:35,930 --> 00:53:36,930
Let's be boyfriends.

949
00:53:38,440 --> 00:53:39,440
What?

950
00:53:39,729 --> 00:53:41,156
This isn't romantic at all.

951
00:53:41,206 --> 00:53:42,726
You're just going to ask me like that?

952
00:53:44,300 --> 00:53:45,452
What do you want me to do?

953
00:53:45,960 --> 00:53:49,304
Do you want me to set off fireworks
to say I love you?

954
00:53:49,970 --> 00:53:51,107
I can't afford that.

955
00:53:53,100 --> 00:53:54,861
I can only promise you that.

956
00:53:56,550 --> 00:54:00,147
I'll never hurt you or be the reason
you come here to curse me out.

957
00:54:07,980 --> 00:54:09,649
That's already really romantic.

958
00:54:29,340 --> 00:54:30,340
Let's be boyfriends.

959
00:54:33,120 --> 00:54:35,120
Okay. Let's try.

960
00:54:59,440 --> 00:55:00,978
I have a boyfriend now!

961
00:55:02,280 --> 00:55:04,203
My boyfriend is freaking cute!

962
00:55:06,280 --> 00:55:07,680
My boyfriend is a flight attendant!

963
00:55:08,630 --> 00:55:09,920
My boyfriend is a bunny!

964
00:55:12,300 --> 00:55:13,987
My boyfriend is a rescuer!

965
00:55:15,870 --> 00:55:17,261
My boyfriend is a Boy Scout!

966
00:55:18,240 --> 00:55:19,243
Isn't that a bit weird?

967
00:55:19,840 --> 00:55:20,972
Yes, but it works.

968
00:55:42,040 --> 00:55:43,329
(Next Episode)
I've been through all of it.

969
00:55:43,353 --> 00:55:44,353
I know the steps.

970
00:55:44,990 --> 00:55:46,769
I don't know what steps
you've been through,

971
00:55:46,800 --> 00:55:47,870
but here's mine.

972
00:55:47,907 --> 00:55:49,046
Once I'm into someone,

973
00:55:49,280 --> 00:55:51,981
I make them feel more loved every day.

974
00:55:52,250 --> 00:55:54,490
Your family still doesn't know
about the thick-brow guy?

975
00:55:55,170 --> 00:55:58,110
Yeah. I was going to tell them,
but I didn't get the chance.

976
00:55:58,640 --> 00:55:59,640
How about this?

977
00:56:00,360 --> 00:56:02,283
If your family hasn't met him yet.

978
00:56:02,550 --> 00:56:04,436
I can pretend to be your captain boyfriend.

979
00:56:04,492 --> 00:56:05,492
Hello.

980
00:56:05,820 --> 00:56:07,113
Sorry, I'm late.

981
00:56:07,150 --> 00:56:08,790
I came straight here as soon as I landed.

982
00:56:09,200 --> 00:56:10,320
Do you really like me?

983
00:56:10,480 --> 00:56:11,480
Yeah.

984
00:56:12,110 --> 00:56:13,966
That's true. I like you
because you're handsome.

985
00:56:13,990 --> 00:56:17,458
I'm going to keep chasing
you until you accept me.
